sequenceDiagram
    participant UI as AutopilotControlPanel
    participant Store as AutopilotStore
    participant API as APIClient
    participant CB as CircuitBreaker API

    Note over UI,Store: 模块 2.4 — 启动参数补全
    UI->>UI: 用户配置 targetChapters / maxAutoChapters / autoApproveMode
    UI->>Store: startAutopilot(novelId, targetChapters, targetWordsPerChapter, maxAutoChapters, autoApproveMode)
    
    par 与 start 并行
        Store->>API: POST /autopilot/{id}/start {max_auto_chapters, target_chapters, target_words_per_chapter}
        API-->>Store: 200 OK
    and 仅当值变化时
        Store->>API: PATCH /novels/{id}/auto-approve-mode {auto_approve_mode: Bool}
        API-->>Store: 200 OK
    end
    
    Store->>Store: startSSEStreams(novelId)
    Store->>Store: startStatusPolling(novelId) ← 自适应退避

    Note over Store,API: 模块 2.5 — 自适应轮询
    loop 轮询循环
        Store->>API: GET /autopilot/{id}/status
        alt 成功
            API-->>Store: 200 status JSON
            Store->>Store: failureCount = 0
            Store->>Store: delay = 4s × 2^min(0,8) = 4s
        alt 404 Not Found
            API-->>Store: 404
            Store->>Store: stoppedForNotFound = true, 停止轮询
        else 其他错误
            API-->>Store: 5xx / 网络错误
            Store->>Store: failureCount += 1
            Store->>Store: delay = 4s × 2^min(fc,8), 上限60s
        end
        Store->>Store: sleep(delay)
    end

    Note over UI,CB: 模块 2.1 — 熔断器字段重写
    UI->>Store: refreshCircuitBreaker(novelId)
    Store->>CB: GET /autopilot/{id}/circuit-breaker
    CB-->>Store: {status, error_count, max_errors, last_error:{message,timestamp,context?}, error_history:[...]}
    Store->>Store: decode AutopilotCircuitBreakerData
    Store-->>UI: circuitBreaker 更新
    UI->>UI: 显示 status / errorCount/maxErrors / lastError.message / errorHistory
